    public class QDLExceptionWithTrace
extends QDLException
    An exception when evaluating a set of statements. This gives the statement number (not the line number, which is close to impossible to determine given how Antlr handles whitespace).

    Created by Jeff Gaynor
    on 11/3/21 at 4:08 PM
